    "causal_summary": "The 007 validation run recorded **19 SKIP** verdicts. 18 of those are copilot-driven CP/discipline stress scenarios — deep-review `07--command-flow-stress-tests` (CP-052..057), deep-research `07--command-flow-stress-tests` (CP-046..051), deep-agent-improvement `08--agent-discipline-stress-tests` (CP-040..045) — that invoke `copilot -p ... --model gpt-5.5`. The `copilot` CLI is org-policy-blocked in this environment (\"Third-party MCP servers disabled by org policy\"), so they cannot run. CP-040..045 carry a **second** blocker: their setup needs the `060-stress-test` fixture, pruned in checkpoint commit `e917f76347`.",
